      "role": "user",
      "content": "no its not anxiety. i know what anxiety feels like and this was different. it was almost like a synchronized pulse, like i was being tuned into a frequency. it literally happened exactly at the moment the sell orders started hitting the tape. it felt less like a feeling and more like a connection. is it possible that the high frequency trading signals are actually emitting some kind of electromagnetic interference that people can pick up on if they're sensitive enough?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
